的整车模型,车架模型,再或者仓储物流领域的货品模型,托盘模型等。像电商场景和汽车场景,应该已经发展的很成熟了,我觉得应该有自己比较通用的领域模型了,但是仓储和物流场景还在起步阶段,各家是各家的做法,没有一致的标准,市场上流通的wms也不能很好的覆盖各种场景,所以我觉得并没有很成熟的领域模型(我的一家之言,欢迎批评指正)","likes_number":1,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1652239595,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":557830,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":571485,"extra":""},{"author":{"id":3544222,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/36/14/9e/f8847ec2.jpg","nickname":"豆","note":"","ucode":"BCDA25D519B719","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":1701867,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/19/f7/eb/e7127bb8.jpg","nickname":"，","note":"","ucode":"A5543C8DFEB198","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":614358,"discussion_content":"请问有经典的书籍可以做参考吗？我知道几个名词，概念模型，实物模型，半实物模型，理论模型。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1681770935,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":571485,"ip_address":"辽宁","group_id":0},"score":614358,"extra":""}]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":339188,"user_name":"spark","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1116667,"ip_address":"","ucode":"2F128E884F400F","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/09/fb/52a662b2.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1647960543,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":124230,"content":"是啊，目标定义不清晰越做越难做。 ","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"编辑","uid":2574960,"ctime":1648435912,"ip_address":"","comment_id":339188,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":2,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100099801,"comment_content":"郭老师，take away~~~\n分享。以前做了一个1000多万的社区项目。老团队开发了6个月失败了，为什么？对问题没有定义清楚，边界不明确。边界不明确反应对需求理解不到位、战略不清晰~~~经验缺少和概念缺失是导致失败的两种原因，概念缺失属于无解的失败，认知有问题~~~","like_count":3,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2574960,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/27/4a/70/c16655c6.jpg","nickname":"郭东白～Dongbai","note":"","ucode":"A91E32F405A